  264 settings made for charge
set type 2 charge -1.2
Setting atom values ...
  528 settings made for charge
pair_style comb
pair_coeff * * ffield.comb Ti O
Reading comb potential file ffield.comb with DATE: 2011-02-22
neighbor 0.5 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes
fix q all qeq/comb 1 0.0001

# 5) Monitoring
thermo 50
thermo_style custom step pe fnorm

# 6) Relax
min_style cg
min_modify dmax 0.005 line quadratic
minimize 1.0e-10 1.0e-10 2000 10000
